Subject: Re: [VB] Things to do while yanking my engine

While you are in there, you also have good inspection access to the rear
rubber brake lines and the condition of the gas tank, the shelf for the
tank, and the battery tray.  Maybe that's all a bit much, but if you
haven't been in there, I would check it all out just to be safe.

Aaron
http://www.singlewheel.com

